   \vec{u}_1\vec{u}_1^T&=\vecd{\frac{\sqrt{2}}{2}}{-\frac{\sqrt{2}}{2}}\left(\frac{\sqrt{2}}{2}\,\,-\frac{\sqrt{2}}{2}\right)
